+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S4-P04-T053 (first-batch high-value A2 pilot; SHADOW)
+
+- Fifty-third task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S4-P04). Onboards the first batch of 10 high-value A2 sources -- functional zones (national new areas, free-trade zones, hi-tech parks, development zones) -- verifying their INCREMENTAL value before scaling. release_mode SHADOW; a selection/pilot task, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/a2_pilot.py provides incremental_signals (a zone's local-action signals minus the A0/A1 baseline of policy/regulation/statistics), verify_official (T033: official non-central .gov.cn; media never official), select_pilot (admit only a zone with incremental value AND a verified official identity; reject no-incremental and non-official zones), a local-action signal taxonomy, and a 2016 cursor per admitted zone. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T053/: a2_pilot_manifest.json, known_gaps.md, recon_signals.json, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T053/test-results/pilot_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): 10 high-value functional zones admitted (Xiongan, Pudong, Zhongguancun, Lingang, Suzhou Industrial Park, Hengqin, Tianfu, Xi'an hi-tech, Liangjiang, Qianhai), each producing real incremental value beyond central/provincial coverage since every admitted zone has at least one local-action signal type (project approval, procurement, pilot, industry-landing, investment, planning) that is not in the A0/A1 baseline; no low-value source is promoted, since a policy-repost zone with zero incremental value and a media source are both rejected through the real selection path; each admitted zone carries an A2 pilot profile, its local-action signals, and a 2016-01 cursor; and three zones (Xiongan, SIP, Hengqin) carry confirmed live local-action signal evidence from recon while the other seven are honestly marked tls_blocked with fetch pending. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S4-P03-T052 (A1 coverage/quality/cost gate; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Fifty-second task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S4-P03). An A1 coverage/quality/cost gate that scores every A1 source touched by the province backfill (T050) and the city cohort (T051) and issues a reversible promote/hold/disable decision. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a scorecard/decision task, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/a1_scorecard.py scores each source on official identity, quality (backfilled documents, content-addressed A1, doc numbers, dates), timeliness (months covered), and cost (0 cloud, dev-env), then decides promote / hold / disable. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S4-P03-T052/: a1_scorecard.json, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (adversarial review CONFIRMED_SOUND; province identity hardened to be derived, not stamped). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S4-P03-T052/test-results/scorecard_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): 22 A1 sources scored at 100% official identity; each decision carries actual evidence, with 3 promoted (Jiangsu, Shandong, Beijing -- each with 3 content-addressed A1 documents with real dates across 2026-06/07), 18 held (the value-verified cities, whose original fetch is pending, so they are NOT promoted on value alone), and 1 disabled (Guangdong, blocked/isolated in T050); the unknown != 0 rule holds since held cities show 0/UNKNOWN documents honestly; and the decisions are reversible since the gate is NOT_DEPLOYED, decisions are bound to a feature flag, no existing production data is rewritten, and rollback is git revert / flag off. Negative controls confirm promotion is earned not given: no city is promoted on value alone and the blocked province disables rather than promotes. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
